g.text: Long division breaks down division into simpler steps for larger numbers.

ol.li: Divide: Divide the first digit(s) by the divisor.
Multiply: Multiply the divisor by the quotient digit.
Subtract: Subtract the result from the dividend.
Bring Down: Bring down the next digit.
Repeat: Repeat until all digits are processed.

ul.li: Long division simplifies division of large numbers.
Steps: Divide, Multiply, Subtract, Bring Down, Repeat.
